rows.label: qst701602_msg0002
rows.name:
If I'm going to participate, I want
to make delicious food and win...

rows.label: qst701602_msg0003
rows.name: That feeling... has come over me...

rows.label: qst701602_msg0004
rows.name:
You're all going back to
the inn to discuss what kind
of food to make, right?

rows.label: qst701602_msg0005
rows.name: I'll prepare as well so I don't lose.

rows.label: qst701602_msg0103
rows.name:
The Adel Cup cooking contest,
shall we begin soon?

rows.label: qst701602_msg0201
rows.name:
How are the preparations
for the cooking contest?

rows.label: qst701602_msg0202
rows.name:
It seems the ingredients
aren't all here yet.

rows.label: qst701602_msg0203
rows.name:
I'm all ready, but I'll wait
until everyone is ready.
